Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 看你正睡得香我就自己先吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡面不煮也蛮好吃的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是觉得庆太的精神状态很差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星期六得要他好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恢复过来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我心脏的融合度似乎不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前有点悬 不过已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融合率是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是短时间内还得待在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我这个原主人不在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏会在完全融合前坏死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个心脏是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太 我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 庆太的心脏在这
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经结下契约了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 庆太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一觉醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信的真相已经开始蚕食我的日常生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了吗 艾克塞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四周的容量多得反常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说主根源被量产了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁 又是为了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能先把他找出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这股容量的引导下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:01.56,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}{\an3}{\be1\bord1}第三集  「同步」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 要你让便当给我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 重点是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们交换了身体的某个部分订立了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是要和被选上的人订的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为了救庆太所以和他订了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是缔结契约的两人能够同步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能发挥自身实力以上的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们元神灵的体质和力量都远胜人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住在异世界的有别于人类的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏交换成功真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 心脏怎么能交换呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才没看见我胸口的伤口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 光凭那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要证据的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 庆太胸口也有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吓到茜姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么她真的是你的救命恩人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报恩就不用了 本来就是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不说话你就得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你能一边凉快去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑是吧 要洗个澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太你真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口有觉得不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周一要去医院看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征司被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真活该
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫他整天吹嘘自己干掉了四个元神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是连征司都打败了 那个少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心力量注多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 这种下位元神灵要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把她找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能见到你了 我的小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是伊吹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是坪田 周末打搅真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说昨晚我们学校有学生被卷进了斗殴中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在附近 一起吃顿饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人住肯定不会好好吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实现在我有朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太 能借一下这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那好吧 要注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没洗澡了 真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑 到那边去换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了 照做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑也累了吧 要躺躺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和庆太一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚缔结契约 我现在的战斗平衡还很混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不对两人的同步做调整 我的能力便会下降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想尽快和庆太同步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一起睡不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我也会住在这
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是庆太的女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你在伺候他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从很小很小的时候就认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以全都吃完吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了那样的事情 真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是第一次坐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前都只能从下面看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 充分休息过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可为什么我也要来呢 明天就考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太现在不可以离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是能稍微离开一点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来我们要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小黑你的衣服都烂得不成样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有什么义务连衣服都帮她买
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变得那么惨还不都是因为她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太到底是怎样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在是我不可缺少的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是不可缺少的人也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时而温柔 时而又很冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我都完全搞糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看那样 其实庆太很热心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不太坦率所以才会被大家误解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得花时间好好亲近了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲近是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 挑喜欢的试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺适合的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件有点太欧式了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺适合的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件也太刺激了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺适合的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 艾克塞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才感觉到了强烈的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及元神灵的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一 记得去医院看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太也吃点早饭补充下能量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去医院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可茜姐说是要去医院的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么跟医生讲呢 他怎么可能会信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在我们两个待在一起比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中午回来 在我回来前别乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主根源的生产还顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然失礼 但您还是不要经常进出这里的好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别因为讨黎真大人欢心而得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了 没有我们狮子神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不过就是个运气好的人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从狮子神一族那得到了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子神一族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这是庆太用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可契约者无论是心还是毛巾都是共用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你好久了 游弋的元神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下位元神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚结契约还无法正常作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就完了吗 再让我玩一会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量…就好像不是自己的身体似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵刺痛是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:15:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的节奏完全乱掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本使不上劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 老老实实跟我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹 我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于你提到过的三位一在系统的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想救你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我起初也不信会有这种系统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是“只有运势好的能活下来”这个设定真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界要是由被选上的人所支配
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就能建立理想的社会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该对这个理想社会做点贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是拯救你的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:17:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了 不是叫你待在家里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里来了下位元神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是下位元神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 小黑说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她订下契约的果然是伊吹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在来接你们的人到之前先在这里等会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来刚结契约的元神灵是这么弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹是我的学生真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个小女孩交上去我的评价也会提高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪呢 伊吹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:18:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太 我要去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们的心意融合 同步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步？要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的觉悟 打倒对手的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会让你们同步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开 伊吹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还期待你能成为根源的完全体—主根源呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和山田那种猴子是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是个好学生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她也为社会尽了一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为产生主根源作出了贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你把自己学生的情报给卖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了做出那些主根源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑 干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他 干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是已经没有战斗的力气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 感觉容量像泉涌般源源不断
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是同步的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去就只能继续战斗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:01.30,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运即力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而人的价值则取决于对运的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.30,0:23:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要利用三位一在系统改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:11.34,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\be1\bord1\fad(800,800)}下一集 「追踪者」
